INSERT INTO `modx_site_tmplvar_contentvalues` VALUES (1,2,1,'assets/savethearctic/css/images/sprite-retina.png'),(2,1,1,'assets/savethearctic/css/images/header-background.jpg'),(3,4,1,'assets/savethearctic/css/images/greenpeaceWhite.png'),(4,3,1,'STYLE GUIDE'),(5,5,3,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"CREATIVE\",\"description\":\"<p>The worlds moving fast. Were adapting with it. Whats fresh, different, and surprising?</p>\",\"image\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/principle-image1.png\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"5\",\"title\":\"CONFRONTATIONAL\",\"description\":\"<p>We\'re peaceful, but that doesn\'t mean we\'re quiet. Speaking truth to power is a big part of who we are.</p>\",\"image\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/Confrontational.png\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"6\",\"title\":\"COURAGEOUS\",\"description\":\"<p>There are many different forms of bravery, from sending a powerful email to climbing a giant skyscraper. Lets celebrate them all.</p>\",\"image\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/principle-image3.png\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"7\",\"title\":\"CONNECTED\",\"description\":\"<p>What happens in the Arctic matters to us all. Were working across vast distances to protect it, and were part of an interconnected movement.</p>\",\"image\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/principle-image4.png\"}]'),(6,6,4,'assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/typography-image.jpg'),(7,7,4,'<p>When creating content for Save The Arctic, the main rule is to make sure its easy to read. When in doubt, stick to Save The Arctic and Open Sans Bold for headers and titles and Open Sans regular for body texts.</p>\r\n<p>Sometimes you need a more informal font, for a lighter touch. Below are a couple good ones weve used before<span>but try not to use more than two fonts at a time.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"w69b-screencastify-mouse\" style=\"-webkit-transform: translate(-100px, -100px) translateZ(0px);\"></div>'),(8,8,4,'<p>The lowercase version of the Save The Arctic font has Arctic glyphs embedded in them. These are a great addition but need to be used carefully. <strong>Make sure theyre used large enough to be able to make out the graphic and use them sparingly in your titles.<br /><br /></strong>Check out this <a title=\"How to use Save The Arctic Font PDF\" href=\"assets/download/font/HowTo.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">PDF</a> for useful information on how to use the Save The Arctic font.</p>\r\n<div class=\"w69b-screencastify-mouse\" style=\"-webkit-transform: translate(-100px, -100px) translateZ(0px);\"></div>'),(9,9,4,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"fontTitle\":\"SAVE THE ARCTIC\",\"fontCss\":\"font-arctic\",\"fontDescription\":\"FOR HEADINGS, TITLES, \\u2018TOUGH\\u2019 BANNERS\",\"fontDownloadText\":\"Save The Arctic\",\"fontFile\":\"assets\\/download\\/font\\/Save_The_Arctic.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"fontTitle\":\"SAvE The ARCtIc\",\"fontCss\":\"font-arctic font-arctic-alt\",\"fontDescription\":\"FOR LOGO &amp; PUBLICATION TITLES\",\"fontDownloadText\":\"Save The Arctic\",\"fontFile\":\"assets\\/download\\/font\\/Save_The_Arctic.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"3\",\"fontTitle\":\"Open Sans Bold\",\"fontCss\":\"font-opensans font-bold\",\"fontDescription\":\"FOR SUBHEADINGS, CALLOUTS, \\u2018SOFT\\u2019 BANNERS\",\"fontDownloadText\":\"Open Sans\",\"fontFile\":\"assets\\/download\\/font\\/Open_Sans_Bold.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"4\",\"fontTitle\":\"Open Sans Regular\",\"fontCss\":\"font-opensans font-normal\",\"fontDescription\":\"FOR BODY TEXT\",\"fontDownloadText\":\"Open Sans\",\"fontFile\":\"assets\\/download\\/font\\/Open_Sans_Regular.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"5\",\"fontTitle\":\"Shadows Into Light\",\"fontCss\":\"font-shadows\",\"fontDescription\":\"INFORMAL FONT\",\"fontDownloadText\":\"Shadows Into Light\",\"fontFile\":\"assets\\/download\\/font\\/Shadows_Into_Light.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"6\",\"fontTitle\":\"Levi Brush\",\"fontCss\":\"font-levi\",\"fontDescription\":\"INFORMAL FONT\",\"fontDownloadText\":\"Levi Brush\",\"fontFile\":\"assets\\/download\\/font\\/Levi_Brush.zip\"}]'),(10,6,5,'assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/color-image.jpg'),(11,7,5,'<p>White is a crucial colour in the Arctic. It is snow, ice and light. It should dominate our campaign materials too.</p>\r\n<p>Darker colours can be used to create contrast and boldness, and to pick out the threat of reckless oil companies.</p>\r\n<div class=\"w69b-screencastify-mouse\" style=\"-webkit-transform: translate(-100px, -100px) translateZ(0px);\"></div>'),(12,8,5,'<p>Brighter colours taken from the palette here can add life and playfulness to the scene, and signal hope and creativity.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Avoid using bright or artificial colours, especially any that are out of place in the Arctic.</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"w69b-screencastify-mouse\" style=\"-webkit-transform: translate(513px, 45px) translateZ(0px);\"></div>'),(13,10,5,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"colourTitle\":\"SNOW\",\"hexColour\":\"FFFFFF\",\"rgbColour\":\"255 \\/ 255 \\/ 255\",\"cmykColour\":\"0 \\/ 0 \\/ 0 \\/ 0\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"colourTitle\":\"OIL\",\"hexColour\":\"1F262A\",\"rgbColour\":\"31 \\/ 38 \\/ 42\",\"cmykColour\":\"78 \\/ 66 \\/ 61 \\/ 68\"}]'),(14,11,5,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"colourTitle\":\"SEAL SKIN\",\"hexColour\":\"8D9C9E\",\"rgbColour\":\"141 \\/ 156 \\/ 158 \",\"cmykColour\":\"48 \\/ 31 \\/ 34 \\/ 1\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"colourTitle\":\"OVERCAST\",\"hexColour\":\"D2DDE4\",\"rgbColour\":\"210 \\/ 221 \\/ 228\",\"cmykColour\":\"16 \\/ 7 \\/ 6 \\/ 0\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"3\",\"colourTitle\":\"POLAR BEAR\",\"hexColour\":\"ECEBE3\",\"rgbColour\":\"236 \\/ 235 \\/ 227\",\"cmykColour\":\"7 \\/ 5 \\/ 9 \\/ 0\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"4\",\"colourTitle\":\"DEEP SEA\",\"hexColour\":\"035880\",\"rgbColour\":\"3 \\/ 88 \\/ 128\",\"cmykColour\":\"96 \\/ 64 \\/ 29 \\/ 11\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"5\",\"colourTitle\":\"ICE SHALLOW\",\"hexColour\":\"00B6C2\",\"rgbColour\":\"0 \\/ 182 \\/ 194\",\"cmykColour\":\"74 \\/ 3 \\/ 26 \\/ 0\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"6\",\"colourTitle\":\"BLUE SKY\",\"hexColour\":\"B8E4F8\",\"rgbColour\":\"184 \\/ 228 \\/ 248\",\"cmykColour\":\"25 \\/ 0 \\/ 1 \\/ 0\"}]'),(15,12,5,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"colourTitle\":\"SUNRISE\",\"hexColour\":\"F59728\",\"rgbColour\":\"245 \\/ 151 \\/ 40\",\"cmykColour\":\"1 \\/ 48 \\/ 95 \\/ 0\",\"colourTitleHover\":\"SUNRISE HOVER\",\"hexColourHover\":\"FFAE17\",\"rgbColourHover\":\"255 \\/ 174 \\/ 23\",\"cmykColourHover\":\"0 \\/ 36 \\/ 98 \\/ 0\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"colourTitle\":\"SUNSET\",\"hexColour\":\"F06E6E\",\"rgbColour\":\"240 \\/ 110 \\/ 110 \",\"cmykColour\":\"1 \\/ 72 \\/ 48 \\/ 0\",\"colourTitleHover\":\"SUNSET HOVER\",\"hexColourHover\":\"EC4A4A\",\"rgbColourHover\":\"236 \\/ 74 \\/ 74 \",\"cmykColourHover\":\"1 \\/ 87 \\/ 71 \\/ 0\"}]'),(16,14,6,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"logoTitle\":\"STANDARD LOGO\",\"logoDescription\":\"When you can, please use this format.\",\"horizontalLogo\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/Standard.png\",\"institutions\":\"[{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"3\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".ai\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Standard_White_ai.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".esp\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Standard_White_eps.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".png\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Standard_White_png.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"4\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".psd\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Standard_White_psd.zip\\\"}]\",\"institutions2\":\"[{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"5\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".ai\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Standard_Black_ai.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".esp\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Standard_Black_eps.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".png\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Standard_Black_png.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"6\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".psd\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Standard_Black_psd.zip\\\"}]\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"logoTitle\":\"SAVETHEARCTIC.ORG\",\"logoDescription\":\"When you want to promote the website, use this format.\",\"horizontalLogo\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/Org.png\",\"institutions\":\"[{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".ai\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Org_White_ai.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".eps\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Org_White_eps.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"3\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".png\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Org_White_png.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"4\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".psd\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Org_White_psd.zip\\\"}]\",\"institutions2\":\"[{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".ai\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Ord_Black_ai.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".eps\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Org_Black_eps.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"3\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".png\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Org_Black_png.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"4\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".psd\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Org_Black_psd.zip\\\"}]\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"3\",\"logoTitle\":\"GLYPH-LESS VERSION\",\"logoDescription\":\"Sometimes its not possible to use the graphic versions, if that is the case you should use the Save The Arctic font and align the text either horizontally or vertically stacked like this.\",\"horizontalLogo\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/Glyphless.png\",\"institutions\":\"[{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".ai\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Glyphless_White_ai.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".eps\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Glyphless_White_eps.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"3\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".png\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Glyphless_White_png.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"4\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".psd\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Glyphless_White_psd.zip\\\"}]\",\"institutions2\":\"[{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".ai\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Glyphless_Black_ai.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".eps\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Glyphless_Black_eps.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"3\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".png\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Glyphless_Black_png.zip\\\"},{\\\"MIGX_id\\\":\\\"4\\\",\\\"BWTitle\\\":\\\".psd\\\",\\\"BWDownloadImage\\\":\\\"assets\\\\/download\\\\/logo\\\\/Glyphless_Black_psd.zip\\\"}]\"}]'),(17,13,6,'<p>Its important to present the campaign logo in a clear, consistent way. But there are a few different ways to do this, depending on language and context. Here are some options:<br /><br /></p>'),(18,7,6,'<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-d6196c6f-c71a-dfd7-335a-965fc7615024\"><span>The logo should ideally always be positioned in the bottom right corner or top left corner of an image. Always allow some margin. The only exception to this is if the body text of an image is centrally aligned then the logo should be too. </span></span></p>'),(19,8,6,'<p>The Save The Arctic logo can stand alone. But if you want to add the Greenpeace logo, they should both be aligned in the same way, with the Save The Arctic logo larger and stacked on top of the Greenpeace one. The Greenpeace logo should only be shown in either black or white on Save The Arctic material.</p>'),(78,64,6,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"greenpeaceTitle\":\".ai\",\"greenpeaceDownloadImage\":\"assets\\/download\\/logo\\/Greenpeace_White_ai.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"greenpeaceTitle\":\".eps\",\"greenpeaceDownloadImage\":\"assets\\/download\\/logo\\/Greenpeace_White_eps.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"3\",\"greenpeaceTitle\":\".png\",\"greenpeaceDownloadImage\":\"assets\\/download\\/logo\\/Greenpeace_White_png.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"4\",\"greenpeaceTitle\":\".psd\",\"greenpeaceDownloadImage\":\"assets\\/download\\/logo\\/Greenpeace_White_psd.zip\"}]'),(79,65,6,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"greenpeaceTitleB\":\".ai\",\"greenpeaceDownloadImageB\":\"assets\\/download\\/logo\\/Greenpeace_Black_ai.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"3\",\"greenpeaceTitleB\":\".eps\",\"greenpeaceDownloadImageB\":\"assets\\/download\\/logo\\/Greenpeace_Black_eps.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"4\",\"greenpeaceTitleB\":\".png\",\"greenpeaceDownloadImageB\":\"assets\\/download\\/logo\\/Greenpeace_Black_png.zip\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"5\",\"greenpeaceTitleB\":\".psd\",\"greenpeaceDownloadImageB\":\"assets\\/download\\/logo\\/Greenpeace_Black_psd.zip\"}]'),(20,15,6,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"logoImages\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/BottomRight.png\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"logoImages\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/TopLeft.png\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"3\",\"logoImages\":\"assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/Center.png\"}]'),(21,6,6,'assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/logo-image.jpg'),(22,16,7,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"iconographyImages\":\"assets\\/savethearctic\\/css\\/images\\/temp\\/shirt.png\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"iconographyImages\":\"assets\\/savethearctic\\/css\\/images\\/temp\\/Icon1.png\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"3\",\"iconographyImages\":\"assets\\/savethearctic\\/css\\/images\\/temp\\/Icon2.png\"}]'),(23,6,7,'assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/iconigraphy-image.jpg'),(24,6,8,'assets/savethearctic/css/images/temp/video-image.jpg'),(94,7,8,'<p>One of our greatest strengths is the visual power of the Arctic and the diversity of the movement that were building to protect it. Photos, videos and other visual assets are a crucial part of explaining this and grabbing peoples attention.</p>\r\n<div class=\"w69b-screencastify-mouse\" style=\"-webkit-transform: translate(-100px, -100px) translateZ(0px);\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"w69b-screencastify-mouse\" style=\"-webkit-transform: translate(-100px, -100px) translateZ(0px);\"></div>'),(26,17,8,'IMAGES'),(27,18,8,'<p>Weve opened up some of the best images from our library for you to adapt and use, and you can download them below. These are for <strong>non-commercial use only,</strong> and please ensure that you credit  Greenpeace/ [Photographers name]. For even more amazing images, please visit the <a href=\"http://photo.greenpeace.org/C.aspx?VP3=CMS&amp;ID=GPIP6\" target=\"_blank\">Greenpeace photo library</a>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"w69b-screencastify-mouse\" style=\"-webkit-transform: translate(-100px, -100px) translateZ(0px);\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"w69b-screencastify-mouse\" style=\"-webkit-transform: translate(-100px, -100px) translateZ(0px);\"></div>'),(28,19,8,'[{\"MIGX_id\":\"1\",\"imageCategoryTitle\":\"LANDSCAPES\",\"categoryImage\":\"assets\\/savethearctic\\/css\\/images\\/temp\\/imageLandscape.png\",\"imageCategoryDropboxUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dropbox.com\\/sh\\/k0r0c1kyfg6ffcj\\/AABsP9CXGOsWSKXMCfJqslPua\\/Landscapes?dl=0\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"2\",\"imageCategoryTitle\":\"WILDLIFE\",\"categoryImage\":\"assets\\/savethearctic\\/css\\/images\\/temp\\/video-image2.jpg\",\"imageCategoryDropboxUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dropbox.com\\/sh\\/k0r0c1kyfg6ffcj\\/AAAHrZeRceC4EmhbhcA7Iq8ia\\/Wildlife?dl=0\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"3\",\"imageCategoryTitle\":\"PEOPLE\",\"categoryImage\":\"assets\\/savethearctic\\/css\\/images\\/temp\\/video-image3.jpg\",\"imageCategoryDropboxUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dropbox.com\\/sh\\/k0r0c1kyfg6ffcj\\/AADVAStY1oIU1zKcATnTHMNia\\/People?dl=0\"},{\"MIGX_id\":\"4\",\"imageCategoryTitle\":\"CLIMATE &amp; INDUSTRY\",\"categoryImage\":\"assets\\/savethearctic\\/css\\/images\\/temp\\/imagesClimateIndustry.png\",\"imageCategoryDropboxUrl\":\